Package info.ephyra.answerselection

Class Summary
AnswerPattern An AnswerPattern is applied to a sentence to extract a PROPERTY object of the type specified in the property field.
AnswerSelection The AnswerSelection component applies Filters to Results to promote promising results, to drop results that are unlikely to answer the question and to derive additional results from the raw results returned by the Searchers.
